70% at the mid 30s and up<br>
100% at the 40+ folks<br>
<br>
5a)  Jewelery from a vendor in the field is often lighter than it's pp value (0.1wt = 4 coins), so keep it till you get back to town, then sell.  Bloodstones or other spell gems are better still since they are stackable and keep your Cleric happy.<br>
<br>
5b)  Carrying some +cha jewelery improves your prices and plenty of bits give +5cha or better for only 0.1wt.<br>
<br>
Purses are the lightest mundane bag (4-slot, small, 0.2wt) and dirt cheap - great for muffins, jewelery, spell reagents and other gems.  Spits are the lightest combine container (6-slot, x-large, 0.2wt).<br>
<br>
When using combine containers (Sewing Kit, Spit etc), right-clicking on the icon to open/close is safest.  [/rude Abashi thinking he could nerf these]<br>
